00:18.801 --> 00:20.063
Cops don't give
a flying fuck

00:20.063 --> 00:21.934
about black or white.

00:21.934 --> 00:23.327
It's all about green.

00:23.327 --> 00:26.722
No one could move dope in Harlem
without the 27th.

00:26.722 --> 00:28.898
