the fucking floor right now!

00:39.039 --> 00:40.431
This is about the heroin.

00:40.431 --> 00:42.085
Colombo's making his play.

00:42.085 --> 00:43.521
You can't control
all of the cops.

00:43.521 --> 00:45.915
I control more than you.

00:45.915 --> 00:48.744
If you can't keep
your cops under control,

00:48.744 --> 00:52.052
