08:28.377 --> 08:31.511
Tell her to bring the girls
home immediately.

08:31.511 --> 08:32.729
Why?

08:32.729 --> 08:33.817
You see what's happening.

08:33.817 --> 08:36.167
We've had threats before.

08:36.167 --> 08:37.255
Bumpy's men are here
to protect us.

08:37.255 --> 08:38.996
We'll be fine.

08:38.996 --> 08:41.433
I just want the children
here with us.

08:41.433 --> 08:44.567
Uh--

08:44.567 --> 08:47.744
We'll discuss this later.

08:47.744 --> 08:50.268
Let's get you home, Elise.

08:50.268 --> 08:53.228
I'm sure you're exhausted
from your long trip.

08:53.228 --> 08:54.272
I am, yes.

08:54.272 --> 08:55.926
