12:16.692 --> 12:18.912
Hello?

12:18.912 --> 12:20.087
Anybody home?

12:20.087 --> 12:23.264
Elise, you're back! Oh!

12:23.264 --> 12:25.222
Oh. God.

12:25.222 --> 12:27.050
