Where's Daddy?

12:32.403 --> 12:34.057
He's out, per usual.

12:34.057 --> 12:36.146
He'll be so excited
you're back.

12:36.146 --> 12:38.322
I must've sent Margaret
20 postcards from Africa.

12:38.322 --> 12:39.802
I hope some have arrived
by now.

12:39.802 --> 12:41.325
I know they have.

12:41.325 --> 12:43.066
